<i>determiner</i>: 전국적 [전국쩍], 범국민적 [범궁민적], 거국적 [거ː국쩍] <i>noun</i>: 범국민적 [범궁민적] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전국적 [전국쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>national; nationwide</dd><br>
<dd>규모나 범위가 온 나라에 걸친.</dd><br>
<dd>Spanning the entire nation in scale or range.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>범국민적 [범궁민적]</dt><br>
<dd>pan-national; nationwide</dd><br>
<dd>국민 모두에 관계되는.</dd><br>
<dd>Pertaining to every person in a nation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거국적 [거ː국쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>nationwide</dd><br>
<dd>모든 국민이 함께 참여하는.</dd><br>
<dd>Involving all the people of a nation.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>범국민적 [범궁민적]</dt><br>
<dd>pan-national; nationwide</dd><br>
<dd>국민 모두에 관계되는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Pertaining to every person in a nation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>